Description
We are one of the largest POS (Point-of-Sale) Developers in Indonesia with close to a thousand user base in one industry alone. We seek to grow our markets into new industries and are looking for a highly motivated individual with strong software consultancy and implementation background to spearhead this effort. Over the years, we have taken pride in our focus on meeting customers’ transactional needs resulting in a POS that offers the most comprehensive functionalities in the market. Our POS also offers a comprehensive reporting system making it easier for business owners to make intelligent business decisions.
Requirements
Lulusan program D3 atau S1, terutama yang memiliki focus dibidang IT ( Information Technology ) Memiliki pengelaman bekerja selama paling sedikit setahun dibidang layanan konsumen Fasih menggunakan program Microsoft Office Memiliki pengetahuan dasar mengenai jaringan (networking) dan cara kerja jaringan internet Mampu berkomunikasi secara jelas dan mudah dimengerti Memiliki semangat kerja dalam tim yang tinggi Jujur, rajin, teliti dan memiliki semangat profesionalisme yang tinggi Menangani keluhan konsumen Memberikan informasi seputar produk Membina hubungan baik dengan konsumen
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified
